div.p:


     The Lord blesse your Maiestie with all his blessings both spirituall and temporall, and who hath giuen you this particular blessing, that your Maiestie may truely say with King Dauid;

Thou hast deliuered me from the contentions of my people, Thou hast preserued mee to be the head ouer nations, the people which I knew not doe serue mee.
     And the Lord further grant that you and your Royall issue may gouerne vs and our posterity in peace and happinesse vnto the worlds end.
